name: intgr-dwh.yml
configuration:
spring:
  jmx:
    default-domain: nttm-dwh-jmx
    enabled: false
  application:
    name: nttm-intgr-dwh
  profiles: develop
    datasource:
      driver-class-name: org.postgresql.Driver
      url: "jdbc:postgresql://postgres-6260:5432/ttm_camunda?ApplicationName=nttm-intgr-dwh"
      username: "postgres"
      password: "1"
  rabbitmq:
    host: rabbitmq-6260
    username: admin
    password: admin
    dwh_events_queue: dwh_events
  jpa:
    database: postgresql
    hibernate:
      ddl-auto: none
    database-platform: org.hibernate.dialect.PostgreSQL95Dialect
    properties:
      hibernate:
        temp:
          use_jdbc_metadata_defaults: false
server:
  port: 8083
app:
  jwt:
    expire: ${JWT_EXPIRE:90000000} #90000000ms = 25hrs
    secret: ${JWT_SECRET_KEY:z%C*F-JaNdRgUkXn2r5u8x/A?D(G+KbPeShVmYq3s6v9y&E)H@McQfTjWnZr4h}
    server: http://localhost:8080/nttm-auth-jwt/api/
dwh:
  task-url: "http://10.31.70.120/FWS/nttm-cmsdwh-adapter/trouble-tickets/task"
  ticket-url: "http://10.31.70.120/FWS/nttm-cmsdwh-adapter/trouble-tickets/ticket"
  login: "nttm_login"
  password: "test"
  test-author-units: 0
  enabled: true
  log-enabled: true
  save-events: true
  save-only-failed: false
  bufferSize: 1
  maxRetryCount: 3
management:
  endpoints:
    web:
      path-mapping:
        prometheus: metrics
      base-path: /
      exposure:
        include: prometheus
  health.solr.enabled: false
logging:
  config: classpath:log4j2-dev.yaml
  level:
    org.hibernate: error
    org.hibernate.SQL: error
    org.zalando.logbook: info
logbook:
  format:
    style: http
  exclude:
    - "**/metrics"
